name: Dead Boy Detectives
overview: Two teen ghosts work alongside a clairvoyant to solve mysteries for their supernatural clientele — until a powerful witch complicates their plans.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Are you a restless spirit trapped in the mortal realm? Call the Dead Boy Detectives. They'll sort out any supernatural mystery — for the right price.

episodes.name: The Case of Crystal Palace
episodes.overview: After coming to the aid of a teen medium with a demonic dilemma, Edwin and Charles head to America to find a missing girl with an unexpected ally.

episodes.name: The Case of the Dandelion Shrine
episodes.overview: Trapped in a sleepy Washington town, the detectives take on a local case: helping Crystal's quirky housemate Niko get rid of her paranormal parasites.

episodes.name: The Case of the Devlin House
episodes.overview: The group tries to free a family of spirits from a nightmarish loop inside a haunted house, but it triggers an extreme case of déjà vu for one detective.

episodes.name: The Case of the Lighthouse Leapers
episodes.overview: The gang looks into a disturbing trend of deaths at a lighthouse. Crystal hears a distinct voice while piecing together clues about the seaside mystery.

episodes.name: The Case of the Two Dead Dragons
episodes.overview: While Crystal, Edwin and Charles investigate the tragic murders of two popular jocks, Niko sets up Jenny and her secret admirer on a butcher shop date.

episodes.name: The Case of the Creeping Forest
episodes.overview: A crisis forces Crystal to improvise on the job as Monty recruits the boys to locate his missing friend — but the eerie case isn't what it seems.

episodes.name: The Case of the Very Long Stairway
episodes.overview: When Edwin gets caught in a frightening situation, Charles relies on his best mate's meticulous notes to find him. A determined Crystal confronts her ex.

episodes.name: The Case of the Hungry Snake
episodes.overview: Crystal reckons with the past after memories come rushing back. With Esther's evil scheme underway, the group is forced to face their deadliest foe yet.
